profile:
J Tree Service Inc has excellent customer service, highly experienced professionals. We provide performance you can trust.

Both Jerry and his climber are ISA Certified, Chainsaw/Hydro certified, and are certified for working around power lines certification. We provide a combined 50 years of experience cutting, trimming and and treating tree-life.

We're eager to be a part of your next project, whether it be small or big!

Call us today at 6133624827 for a free estimate!

profile:
Professional, expert advice on trees, plants, and landscapes by Ontario Certified Arborist & Horticulturist Jim Althouse. From root tips to tree tops, holistic tree health care since 1981. Safe removals, trimming and cabling by climbing arborist "No Spurs" MacLean, who goes where bucket trucks can't. Member of the International Society of Arboriculture & Cornwall Horticultural Society. Pest ID & control. Insured & WSIB. Tree planting & landscape rejuventation. 
To save a tree, call the "TreeDoc".
